        "- If Train RMSE ≈ Test RMSE and both are acceptable → **Good model, no overfit or underfit.**\n",
        "- If Train RMSE << Test RMSE (significant gap) → **Overfit (High Variance).**\n",
        "- If both Train and Test RMSE are high → **Underfit (High Bias).**\n",
