        "---\n",
        "\n",
        "# Conclusion\n",
        "\n",
        "This notebook implemented a **two-stage flight delay prediction system** using supervised machine learning at the airport-day level, using only techniques covered in the course:\n",
        "\n",
        "**Stage 1 — Classification (Logistic Regression):**\n",
        "- Predicts whether an airport-day will experience a delay of 15 minutes or more (`target_delayed_15`).\n",
        "- Evaluated using Accuracy, Precision, Recall, F1-score, and the Confusion Matrix.\n",
        "- Training and testing metrics were compared to check for overfit or underfit.\n",
        "\n",
        "**Stage 2 — Regression (Linear Regression):**\n",
        "- Predicts the expected number of delay minutes (`target_delay_minutes`).\n",
        "- Evaluated using MAE, MSE, RMSE, and R² Score.\n",
        "- Training and testing metrics were compared to check for overfit or underfit.\n",
        "\n",
        "**Key design decisions:**\n",
        "\n",
        "- A **random 80/20 `train_test_split`** with a fixed `random_state` for reproducibility, like every example in the slides.\n",
